  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the effect on intraocular pressure in glaucoma patients
      using the TravAlert dosing aid with or without the Eyot drop guider and with or without
      additional patient education.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
